Mini BDM Pod
============ 
A small and inexpensive D-Bug12Xv5 Pod for Freescale's S12(X) microcontrollers.

RevB:
=====
Files:
"Mini BDM Pod RevB.sch"               - Schematic (Eagle 6.1.0)
"Mini BDM Pod RevB.brd"               - PCB layout (Eagle 6.1.0)
"Mini BDM Pod RevB.Gerber.zip"        - PCB layout (Gerber)
"Mini BDM Pod RevB.svg"               - Enclosure (for laser cutting service) 
"Mini BDM Pod RevB BOM.txt"           - Bill of Materials
"Mini BDM Pod RevB Schematic.pdf"     - Schematic
"Mini BDM Pod RevB Mounting Plan.pdf" - Assembly diagram

RevA (obsolete!!!):
===================
"Mini BDM Pod RevA.sch"               - Schematic (Eagle 6.1.0)
"Mini BDM Pod RevA.brd"               - PCB layout (Eagle 6.1.0)
"Mini BDM Pod RevA.Gerber.zip"        - PCB layout (Gerber)
"Mini BDM Pod RevA.svg"               - Enclosure (for laser cutting service) 
"Mini BDM Pod RevA BOM.txt"           - Bill of Materials
"Mini BDM Pod RevA Schematic.pdf"     - Schematic
"Mini BDM Pod RevA Mounting Plan.pdf" - Assembly diagram

==> RevA cantains a severe layout bug. The MAX3373E level shifter incorrectly connected. Therefore the PCB may only be used for 5V targets, ommiting and bypassing the level shifter. 


